<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.2.4">
<l>eñca lililaṅ kaikkiṟai yeṅkōṉ ṟaṉṉai muṉpaṇin teṅkaḷkaṇ mukappē</l>
<l>nañcu tāṉarak karkuṭik keṉṟu naṅkai yaiyavaṉ tampiyē coṉṉāṉ</l>
<l>viñcai vāṉavar vēṇṭiṟṟē paṭṭōm vēri vārpoḻil māmayi laṉṉa</l>
<l>vañca lōtiyaik koṇṭuna ṭami ṉañci ṉōmtaṭam poṅkattam poṅkō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Bowing before to our king, the master of flawless Laṅkā, his younger brother,</l>
<l>Before our eyes said of the lady, “She is the bane of our demon clan.”</l>
<l>We endured what the learned celestials wished.</l>
<l rend="indent">Take the [lady with] dark hair of five [qualities],</l>
<l>Like [the tail of] a dark peacock in a grove where nectar flows, and go!</l>
<l rend="indent">We are frightened. Oh, it’s a turbulent road; it’s a turbulent path!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
